snippet.textDisplay: I learned to ski in 2020, took one lesson and hit the slopes at mount bachelor for a school trip the following week and it was definitely an adventure. Fell down but learned to ski better. Especially in crappy conditions. Now I’m getting more comfortable doing jumps even thought the skis and ski boots are a lot heavier than a snowboard lol.
